* &quot;Party with the Rovers&quot; – VHS, 1988
* &quot;The Irish Rovers Silver Anniversary&quot; – CBC, 1989
* &quot;The Irish Rovers Celebrate 30 Years&quot; – CBC,1994
* &quot;Celebrate! The First Thirty Years&quot; – VHS, 1994
