formula_79

The Rodrigues formula for the Hermite polynomials can be written as
formula_80

Similar formulae hold for many other sequences of orthogonal functions arising from Sturm–Liouville equations, and these are also called the Rodrigues formula (or Rodrigues&#x27; type formula) for that case, especially when the resulting sequence is polynomial.

